PTHREADS --->> (POSIX THREADS) --->> PORTABLE OPERATING SYSTEM INTERFACE THREADS

KEY FEATURES IN PTHREAD.H --->>

1. pthread_create() --->> Create a new thread
2. pthread_exit() --->> Exit a thread
3. pthread_join() --->> Wait for thread to finish
4. pthread_mutex_init() --->> Initialize a Mutex
5. pthread_mutex_lock() --->> Lock a Mutex
6. pthread_mutex_unlock() --->> Unlock a Mutex
7. pthread_mutex_detroy() --->> Destroy a Mutex


RACE CONDITION --->> Condition when two threads access a shared variable at the same time without SYNCHRONIZATION.
